 A Nigerian woman has revealed how her boyfriend ended their relationship in an unexpected and costly way. He sent her a gift of an iPhone 13 Pro Max, along with a breakup letter hidden inside the phone pack. In a viral video, the lady is seen unboxing her gift when she notices the short note, which she interprets as the end of her relationship. The short note read; ”It’s over between us” She posted the clip and captioned it; ”Breakfast well served with iPhone 13 Pro Max” Watch the video below; In other news; Opeyemi Falegan, Nkechi Blessing Sunday’s ex-boyfriend, has denied claims that he apologized to her because he wants her back. On Monday, May 9, Opeyemi had an IG live session with OAP DaddyFreeze in which he publicly apologized to Nkechi for dragging them over their breakup. He expressed his love for her and asked her to forgive him.